Reverse an array in java using for loop

[Reverse an array in java using for loop](https://www.flowerbrackets.com/reverse-an-array-in-java-using-for-loop/)

 Hereâ€™s the program to reverse an array using for loop.

public class ReverseArrayUsingForLoop 
{
   public static void main(String[] args) 
   {
      int[] arrNumbers = new int[]{2, 4, 6, 8, 10};  
      System.out.println("Given array: ");  
      for(int a = 0; a < arrNumbers.length; a++)
      {
         System.out.print(arrNumbers[a] + " ");
      }
      System.out.println("Reverse array: ");
      // looping array in reverse order
      for(int a = arrNumbers.length - 1; a >= 0; a--) 
      {  
         System.out.print(arrNumbers[a] + " ");  
      }
   }
}


Output:

Given array:
2 4 6 8 10
Reverse array:
10 8 6 4 2
